{
  "book": "1nephi",
  "bookName": "1 Nephi",
  "chapter": 22,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "ddDFRErfhdc2asyySOG5",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Samuel"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 556.973,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 4.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now it came to pass that after I, Nephi, had read these things",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 4.824,
      "end": 8.539,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which were engraven upon the plates of brass,",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 8.719,
      "end": 11.366,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my brethren came unto me and said unto me:",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 11.546,
      "end": 14.193,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "What meaneth these things which ye have read?",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 14.373,
      "end": 16.463,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, are they to be understood",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 16.643,
      "end": 19.011,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to things which are spiritual,",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 19.191,
      "end": 20.724,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall come to pass",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 20.904,
      "end": 23.272,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to the spirit and not the flesh?",
      "verse": "22:1",
      "lineIndex": 8
    },
    {
      "start": 23.952,
      "end": 26.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Nephi, said unto them:",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 26.361,
      "end": 30.587,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold they were manifest unto the prophet by the voice of the Spirit;",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 30.767,
      "end": 32.3,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for by the Spirit",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 32.48,
      "end": 35.174,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are all things made known unto the prophets,",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 35.354,
      "end": 40.416,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall come upon the children of men according to the flesh.",
      "verse": "22:2",
      "lineIndex": 13
    },
    {
      "start": 41.096,
      "end": 44.347,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the things of which I have read",
      "verse": "22:3",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 44.527,
      "end": 48.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are things pertaining to things both temporal and spiritual;",
      "verse": "22:3",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 48.376,
      "end": 51.952,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for it appears that the house of Israel, sooner or later,",
      "verse": "22:3",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 52.132,
      "end": 55.383,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "will be scattered upon all the face of the earth,",
      "verse": "22:3",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 55.563,
      "end": 57.467,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also among all nations.",
      "verse": "22:3",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 58.147,
      "end": 61.723,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And behold, there are many who are already lost",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 61.903,
      "end": 64.829,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the knowledge of those who are at Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 65.009,
      "end": 68.167,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Yea, the more part of all the tribes have been led away;",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 68.347,
      "end": 72.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they are scattered to and fro upon the isles of the sea;",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 22
    },
    {
      "start": 72.289,
      "end": 74.704,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and whither they are none of us knoweth,",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 74.884,
      "end": 77.903,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "save that we know that they have been led away.",
      "verse": "22:4",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 78.583,
      "end": 80.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And since they have been led away,",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 80.946,
      "end": 84.336,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "these things have been prophesied concerning them,",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 84.516,
      "end": 89.253,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also concerning all those who shall hereafter be scattered and be confounded,",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 89.433,
      "end": 91.755,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of the Holy One of Israel;",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 91.935,
      "end": 94.721,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for against him will they harden their hearts;",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 29
    },
    {
      "start": 94.901,
      "end": 98.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, they shall be scattered among all nations",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 98.657,
      "end": 100.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall be hated of all men.",
      "verse": "22:5",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 101.427,
      "end": 104.817,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Nevertheless, after they shall be nursed by the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 104.997,
      "end": 108.155,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lord has lifted up his hand upon the Gentiles",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 108.335,
      "end": 110.564,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and set them up for a standard,",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 110.744,
      "end": 113.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their children have been carried in their arms,",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 113.803,
      "end": 116.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their daughters have been carried upon their shoulders,",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 116.955,
      "end": 120.066,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold these things of which are spoken are temporal;",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 37
    },
    {
      "start": 120.246,
      "end": 123.543,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus are the covenants of the Lord with our fathers;",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 123.723,
      "end": 126.045,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it meaneth us in the days to come,",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 126.225,
      "end": 128.268,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all our brethren",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 128.448,
      "end": 130.631,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "22:6",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 131.311,
      "end": 135.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it meaneth that the time cometh that after all the house of Israel",
      "verse": "22:7",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 135.856,
      "end": 138.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "have been scattered and confounded,",
      "verse": "22:7",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 138.312,
      "end": 142.584,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God will raise up a mighty nation among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "22:7",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 142.764,
      "end": 145.411,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even upon the face of this land;",
      "verse": "22:7",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 145.591,
      "end": 148.238,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by them shall our seed be scattered.",
      "verse": "22:7",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 148.918,
      "end": 152.122,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after our seed is scattered the Lord God will proceed",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 152.302,
      "end": 155.274,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to do a marvelous work among the Gentiles,",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 155.454,
      "end": 158.055,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be of great worth unto our seed;",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 158.235,
      "end": 160.139,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, it is likened",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 160.319,
      "end": 163.152,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto their being nourished by the Gentiles",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 163.332,
      "end": 166.676,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and being carried in their arms and upon their shoulders.",
      "verse": "22:8",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 167.356,
      "end": 170.235,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall also be of worth unto the Gentiles;",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 54
    },
    {
      "start": 170.415,
      "end": 172.644,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and not only unto the Gentiles",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 172.824,
      "end": 175.1,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "but unto all the house of Israel,",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 175.28,
      "end": 177.741,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the making known of the covenants",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 177.921,
      "end": 180.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "of the Father of heaven unto Abraham, saying:",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 181.027,
      "end": 184.417,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "In thy seed shall all the kindreds of the earth be blessed.",
      "verse": "22:9",
      "lineIndex": 59
    },
    {
      "start": 185.097,
      "end": 187.837,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I would, my brethren, that ye should know",
      "verse": "22:10",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 188.017,
      "end": 190.989,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that all the kindreds of the earth cannot be blessed",
      "verse": "22:10",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 191.169,
      "end": 195.024,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unless he shall make bare his arm in the eyes of the nations.",
      "verse": "22:10",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 195.704,
      "end": 197.933,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the Lord God will proceed",
      "verse": "22:11",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 198.113,
      "end": 201.41,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to make bare his arm in the eyes of all the nations,",
      "verse": "22:11",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 201.59,
      "end": 204.748,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in bringing about his covenants and his gospel",
      "verse": "22:11",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 204.928,
      "end": 207.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto those who are of the house of Israel.",
      "verse": "22:11",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 208.162,
      "end": 212.109,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he will bring them again out of captivity,",
      "verse": "22:12",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 212.289,
      "end": 216.469,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be gathered together to the lands of their inheritance;",
      "verse": "22:12",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 216.649,
      "end": 221.014,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be brought out of obscurity and out of darkness;",
      "verse": "22:12",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 221.194,
      "end": 225.327,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall know that the Lord is their Savior and their Redeemer,",
      "verse": "22:12",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 225.507,
      "end": 227.132,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Mighty One of Israel.",
      "verse": "22:12",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 227.812,
      "end": 230.923,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the blood of that great and abominable church,",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 231.103,
      "end": 233.286,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is the whore of all the earth,",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 233.466,
      "end": 235.602,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall turn upon their own heads;",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 235.782,
      "end": 238.104,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they shall war among themselves,",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 238.284,
      "end": 240.745,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the sword of their own hands",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 240.925,
      "end": 242.922,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall fall upon their own heads,",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 243.102,
      "end": 246.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall be drunken with their own blood.",
      "verse": "22:13",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 246.986,
      "end": 249.819,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And every nation which shall war against thee,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 249.999,
      "end": 251.485,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "O house of Israel,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 251.665,
      "end": 254.126,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be turned one against another,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 82
    },
    {
      "start": 254.306,
      "end": 257.371,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they shall fall into the pit which they digged",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 257.551,
      "end": 259.734,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to ensnare the people of the Lord.",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 259.914,
      "end": 263.165,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And all that fight against Zion shall be destroyed,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 263.345,
      "end": 265.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and that great whore,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 265.197,
      "end": 268.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "who hath perverted the right ways of the Lord,",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 268.303,
      "end": 272.715,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, that great and abominable church, shall tumble to the dust",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 272.895,
      "end": 274.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and great shall be the fall of it.",
      "verse": "22:14",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 275.665,
      "end": 278.962,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, saith the prophet, the time cometh speedily",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 279.142,
      "end": 281.696,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that Satan shall have no more power",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 281.876,
      "end": 284.291,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "over the hearts of the children of men;",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 284.471,
      "end": 286.282,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the day soon cometh",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 286.462,
      "end": 289.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that all the proud and they who do wickedly",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 94
    },
    {
      "start": 289.382,
      "end": 291.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be as stubble;",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 291.187,
      "end": 292.72,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the day cometh",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 292.9,
      "end": 294.386,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they must be burned.",
      "verse": "22:15",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 295.066,
      "end": 296.831,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the time soon cometh",
      "verse": "22:16",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 297.011,
      "end": 299.333,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the fulness of the wrath of God",
      "verse": "22:16",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 299.513,
      "end": 302.95,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be poured out upon all the children of men;",
      "verse": "22:16",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 303.13,
      "end": 304.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he will not suffer",
      "verse": "22:16",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 304.889,
      "end": 307.211,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the wicked shall destroy the righteous.",
      "verse": "22:16",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 307.891,
      "end": 311.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, he will preserve the righteous by his power,",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 311.182,
      "end": 314.711,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be that the fulness of his wrath must come,",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 314.891,
      "end": 317.074,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the righteous be preserved,",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 317.254,
      "end": 320.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even unto the destruction of their enemies by fire.",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 320.731,
      "end": 323.192,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, the righteous need not fear;",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 323.372,
      "end": 325.322,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for thus saith the prophet,",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 325.502,
      "end": 327.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they shall be saved,",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 327.307,
      "end": 329.443,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be as by fire.",
      "verse": "22:17",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 330.123,
      "end": 332.306,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, my brethren, I say unto you,",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 332.486,
      "end": 334.854,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that these things must shortly come;",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 335.034,
      "end": 336.984,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, even blood, and fire,",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 337.164,
      "end": 339.114,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and vapor of smoke must come;",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 339.294,
      "end": 342.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it must needs be upon the face of this earth;",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 342.818,
      "end": 345.651,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it cometh unto men according to the flesh",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 345.831,
      "end": 348.942,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they will harden their hearts",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 349.122,
      "end": 351.398,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "against the Holy One of Israel.",
      "verse": "22:18",
      "lineIndex": 118
    },
    {
      "start": 352.078,
      "end": 354.632,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For behold, the righteous shall not perish;",
      "verse": "22:19",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 354.812,
      "end": 356.995,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for the time surely must come",
      "verse": "22:19",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 357.175,
      "end": 360.426,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that all they who fight against Zion shall be cut off.",
      "verse": "22:19",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 361.106,
      "end": 364.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord will surely prepare a way for his people,",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 364.397,
      "end": 367.091,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "unto the fulfilling of the words of Moses,",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 367.271,
      "end": 369.036,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which he spake, saying:",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 369.216,
      "end": 373.303,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "A prophet shall the Lord your God raise up unto you, like unto me;",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 373.483,
      "end": 377.198,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "him shall ye hear in all things whatsoever he shall say unto you.",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 377.378,
      "end": 379.514,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And it shall come to pass that",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 379.694,
      "end": 382.248,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "all those who will not hear that prophet",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 382.428,
      "end": 384.982,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall be cut off from among the people.",
      "verse": "22:20",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 385.662,
      "end": 388.216,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, declare unto you",
      "verse": "22:21",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 388.396,
      "end": 392.668,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that this prophet of whom Moses spake was the Holy One of Israel;",
      "verse": "22:21",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 392.848,
      "end": 396.517,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, he shall execute judgment in righteousness.",
      "verse": "22:21",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 397.197,
      "end": 399.38,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the righteous need not fear,",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 399.56,
      "end": 402.254,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they are those who shall not be confounded.",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 402.434,
      "end": 404.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But it is the kingdom of the devil,",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 404.982,
      "end": 406.7,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which shall be built up",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 406.88,
      "end": 410.363,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among the children of men, which kingdom is established",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 410.543,
      "end": 412.772,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "among them which are in the flesh\u2014",
      "verse": "22:22",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 413.452,
      "end": 418.932,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For the time speedily shall come that all churches which are built up to get gain,",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 419.112,
      "end": 422.641,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all those who are built up to get power over the flesh,",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 422.821,
      "end": 427.093,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those who are built up to become popular in the eyes of the world,",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 427.273,
      "end": 431.917,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and those who seek the lusts of the flesh and the things of the world,",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 432.097,
      "end": 434.326,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and to do all manner of iniquity;",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 434.506,
      "end": 438.546,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yea, in fine, all those who belong to the kingdom of the devil",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 438.726,
      "end": 441.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "are they who need fear, and tremble, and quake;",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 442.157,
      "end": 445.268,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they are those who must be brought low in the dust;",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 445.448,
      "end": 448.188,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they are those who must be consumed as stubble;",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 448.368,
      "end": 451.805,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and this is according to the words of the prophet.",
      "verse": "22:23",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 452.485,
      "end": 454.528,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the time cometh speedily",
      "verse": "22:24",
      "lineIndex": 150
    },
    {
      "start": 454.708,
      "end": 458.191,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the righteous must be led up as calves of the stall,",
      "verse": "22:24",
      "lineIndex": 151
    },
    {
      "start": 458.371,
      "end": 460.786,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Holy One of Israel must reign",
      "verse": "22:24",
      "lineIndex": 152
    },
    {
      "start": 460.966,
      "end": 462.777,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in dominion, and might,",
      "verse": "22:24",
      "lineIndex": 153
    },
    {
      "start": 462.957,
      "end": 464.907,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and power, and great glory.",
      "verse": "22:24",
      "lineIndex": 154
    },
    {
      "start": 465.587,
      "end": 467.491,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he gathereth his children",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 155
    },
    {
      "start": 467.671,
      "end": 470.411,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the four quarters of the earth;",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 156
    },
    {
      "start": 470.591,
      "end": 472.541,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he numbereth his sheep,",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 157
    },
    {
      "start": 472.721,
      "end": 474.207,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they know him;",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 158
    },
    {
      "start": 474.387,
      "end": 477.638,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and there shall be one fold and one shepherd;",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 159
    },
    {
      "start": 477.818,
      "end": 479.536,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he shall feed his sheep,",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 160
    },
    {
      "start": 479.716,
      "end": 482.131,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and in him they shall find pasture.",
      "verse": "22:25",
      "lineIndex": 161
    },
    {
      "start": 482.811,
      "end": 485.551,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And because of the righteousness of his people,",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 162
    },
    {
      "start": 485.731,
      "end": 487.31,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Satan has no power;",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 163
    },
    {
      "start": 487.49,
      "end": 491.391,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "wherefore, he cannot be loosed for the space of many years;",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 164
    },
    {
      "start": 491.571,
      "end": 493.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he hath no power",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 165
    },
    {
      "start": 493.376,
      "end": 495.652,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "over the hearts of the people,",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 166
    },
    {
      "start": 495.832,
      "end": 497.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for they dwell in righteousness,",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 167
    },
    {
      "start": 498.148,
      "end": 500.47,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Holy One of Israel reigneth.",
      "verse": "22:26",
      "lineIndex": 168
    },
    {
      "start": 501.15,
      "end": 503.518,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, I, Nephi, say unto you",
      "verse": "22:27",
      "lineIndex": 169
    },
    {
      "start": 503.698,
      "end": 506.856,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that all these things must come according to the flesh.",
      "verse": "22:27",
      "lineIndex": 170
    },
    {
      "start": 507.536,
      "end": 510.74,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But, behold, all nations, kindreds, tongues, and people",
      "verse": "22:28",
      "lineIndex": 171
    },
    {
      "start": 510.92,
      "end": 513.985,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "shall dwell safely in the Holy One of Israel",
      "verse": "22:28",
      "lineIndex": 172
    },
    {
      "start": 514.165,
      "end": 516.812,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it so be that they will repent.",
      "verse": "22:28",
      "lineIndex": 173
    },
    {
      "start": 517.492,
      "end": 519.35,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Nephi, make an end;",
      "verse": "22:29",
      "lineIndex": 174
    },
    {
      "start": 519.53,
      "end": 523.524,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I durst not speak further as yet concerning these things.",
      "verse": "22:29",
      "lineIndex": 175
    },
    {
      "start": 524.204,
      "end": 528.012,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, my brethren, I would that ye should consider",
      "verse": "22:30",
      "lineIndex": 176
    },
    {
      "start": 528.192,
      "end": 530.468,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the things which have been written",
      "verse": "22:30",
      "lineIndex": 177
    },
    {
      "start": 530.648,
      "end": 534.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "upon the plates of brass are true; and they testify",
      "verse": "22:30",
      "lineIndex": 178
    },
    {
      "start": 534.265,
      "end": 537.284,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that a man must be obedient to the commandments of God.",
      "verse": "22:30",
      "lineIndex": 179
    },
    {
      "start": 537.964,
      "end": 540.007,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, ye need not suppose",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 180
    },
    {
      "start": 540.187,
      "end": 542.973,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I and my father are the only ones",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 181
    },
    {
      "start": 543.153,
      "end": 545.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that have testified, and also taught them.",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 182
    },
    {
      "start": 546.027,
      "end": 549.51,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Wherefore, if ye shall be obedient to the commandments,",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 183
    },
    {
      "start": 549.69,
      "end": 551.315,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and endure to the end,",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 184
    },
    {
      "start": 551.495,
      "end": 553.771,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "ye shall be saved at the last day.",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 185
    },
    {
      "start": 553.951,
      "end": 555.298,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And thus it is.",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 186
    },
    {
      "start": 555.478,
      "end": 556.314,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "22:31",
      "lineIndex": 187
    }
  ]
}